/sys/:Kernel Core Files and Modules
/usr/:User Space Root
     --> /usr/home/:User Home Directories
          --> /usr/home/guest/:Default Guest User Directory
/bin/:System Binaries and Configurations
     --> /bin/config/:System and User Configurations
          --> /bin/config/services.ini:Service Manager Configuration
          --> /bin/config/guest/profile.ini:User Profile Configuration
     --> /bin/pkg/:Software Package Repository
          --> /bin/pkg/bspm:BrightS Package Manager
          --> /bin/pkg/.db/:Package Database
     --> /bin/firmware/:Firmware Packages and Updates
     --> /bin/runtime/:Runtime Environments and Toolchains
          --> /bin/runtime/rust/:Rust Compiler (rustc, cargo)
          --> /bin/runtime/c/:C Compiler (gcc, clang, make)
          --> /bin/runtime/python/:Python Interpreter (python3, pip)
/mnt/:Mount Points for External Devices
     --> /mnt/drive/:Mounted Storage Devices
     --> /mnt/input/:Input Device Interfaces
          --> /mnt/input/keyboard/:Keyboard Devices
          --> /mnt/input/mouse/:Mouse Devices
          --> /mnt/input/touchpad/:Touchpad Devices
          --> /mnt/input/camera/:Camera Devices
          --> /mnt/input/biometric/:Biometric Input Devices
     --> /mnt/output/:Output Device Interfaces
/tmp/:Temporary Files (RAM-based)
/swp/:Swap Space
/var/:Variable System Data
     --> /var/log/:System Log Files
          --> /var/log/system.log:System Logging Daemon Output
     --> /var/run/:Runtime Process Information
          --> /var/run/*.pid:Daemon Process ID Files

Runtime Environment Components:
/bin/shell:BrightS Command Shell
/bin/init:Service Manager (PID 1)
/bin/syslogd:System Logging Daemon
/bin/dhcpd:DHCP Client Daemon

Service Configuration Format:
[service_name]
description=Service Description
command=/path/to/executable
type=daemon|oneshot|forking|notify
restart=yes|no
restart_delay=milliseconds
depends_on=service1,service2

